Megatron tried to tighten his grip, and brought another knee upwards,
now holding Unitron in mid-air, by staying in flight. His recoil cnnon
on his back, folded down, underneath his right arm, and towards Unitron,
and with a Sadistci smile, Megatron smiled, and fired.
